Sea la curva 
\begin_inset Formula $\Cinf$
\end_inset 

 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma$
\end_inset 

 dada por 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma:\left\{ x^{\mu}\left[t\right]:t\in\cR{}\right\} $
\end_inset 

.
